    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/f249a0e19dc9442b6d88f0b6b93c843d.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你好，我是 <strong>KoKo</strong>。我是 <strong>AmaZoo</strong> 的新 <strong>拣货员</strong>。我的工作是把这些 <strong>箱子</strong> 放到正确的地方——至少，我想是这样。我还没有得到所有的 <strong>指示</strong>，而且这里有些我不太确定的 <strong>危险物品</strong>。你能帮我搬动这些 <strong>箱子</strong> 并找到出口吗？我真的等不及想结束这漫长的 <strong>一天</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/bbd28c8e3b745012242bdfa9f119b988.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/f53b4ee39862f3f2cc6a7c9bb245850b.poster.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/f53b4ee39862f3f2cc6a7c9bb245850b.webm?t=1745228866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/f53b4ee39862f3f2cc6a7c9bb245850b.mp4?t=1745228866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AmaZoo 是一款渐进式且充满变化的益智游戏，灵感来自经典的《推箱子》，但采用了横版视角，致敬复古的 2D 游戏风格。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将享受直观又引人入胜的体验，解开 100 多个精心设计的谜题，每一关都旨在挑战你的逻辑思维。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标是移动并整理各种不同类型的箱子，为自己清出通往出口的道路，并进入下一关。但要小心——有些箱子行为难以预测，一个失误就可能让原本简单的任务变得棘手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/dabd755dc1b23ba099d58612ff2760c2.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/bf5c3df411d6f370d944fb31acd9157c.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有几种不同类型的 <strong>“箱子”</strong>，每种都有独特的特性和机制。作为 <strong>KoKo</strong>，你需要利用你的技巧来 <strong>携带</strong>、<strong>丢下</strong>、<strong>扔</strong>、<strong>堆叠</strong>、<strong>跳跃</strong> 和 <strong>攀爬</strong>，并在手中拿着箱子。如果箱子挡住了你的路或让你抓狂，别犹豫，赶紧 <strong>踢开它</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/111eda824c10ae181cbff45ffe070c8a.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AmaZoo</strong> 的仓库绝对不安全——远远不符合 <strong>人类安全标准</strong>。你将遇到 <strong>高耸的楼梯</strong>、<strong>压缩机</strong>、<strong>故障的机器</strong>、<strong>尖刺</strong>、<strong>激光</strong>，甚至还有 <strong>爆炸性危险</strong>。小心，<strong>KoKo</strong>—— <strong>职场事故</strong> 随时可能发生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/7ea5daad6e3fd737aa1fd1902824ec21.avif?t=1745228866\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别让平静的氛围欺骗了你——随着游戏进展， <strong>谜题</strong> 会越来越具挑战性，旨在极限考验你的 <strong>逻辑思维</strong> 和 <strong>创造力</strong>。你能应对挑战吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢挑战，可以重新挑战关卡，刷新自己的 <strong>纪录</strong>！但记住： <strong>优化</strong> 工作是关键。</p>",
